; Test fn_set_commodity_price to exercise lines 953-956 of report.cc
; set_commodity_price(amount, datetime, price) sets a price on the commodity

2024/01/01 Buy Stock
    Assets:Brokerage    10 AAPL
    Assets:Cash         -1500 EUR

test reg Assets:Brokerage --format "%(set_commodity_price(amount, now, 200 EUR))%(market(amount, now))\n"
2000 EUR
end test
